</div>               <h1 class="firstHeading"><span class="redfont">C</span>hanges in Guantanamo Bay SOP manual (2003-2004)</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikileaks</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p><b>JULIAN ASSANGE</b> and <b>DANIEL MATHEWS</b> with <b>EMI MACLEAN</b>, <b>MARC FALKOFF</b>, <b>REBECCA DICK</b> and <b>BETH GILSON</b> (habeas counsel). <br />
Tuesday December 3, 2007
</p>
