<p>See also the as yet unreported document
</p>
<ul><li> <a href="/wiki/Detainee_Operations_in_a_Joint_Environment" title="Detainee Operations in a Joint Environment">Detainee Operations in a Joint Environment</a> - rush-released leak
</li></ul>
<p>Sample quote from this unanalyzed document:
</p><p><i>
(1) On-board the aircraft:
</p>
<dl><dd>(a)Detainees will be shackled (cuffed) to leg and wrist irons connected to belly irons and the aircraft. 
</dd><dd>(b)Detainees will be blindfolded at all times. 
</dd><dd>(c)Detainee’s gloves will remain in place at all times. 
</dd><dd>(d)Detainees will have ear/hearing muffs on.
</dd></dl>
